content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 ยง 59.3 - Prohibition on use of water craft propelled by gasoline powered motors at fishing access sites

State Regulations

No person may launch or use a boat, canoe or other water
craft equipped with a gasoline powered motor at the Laurel Lake fishing access
site, Town of Southold, Suffolk County. Notes
